bi niya. Tae. Buti hindi ako nakain nung mais kunti nabilaukan nako. Aish. Nakatingin din siya saken. Hindi ako makapagsalita. Walang lumalabas na salita sa bibig ko. Anobayan. -___________-'

 

"Charlotte, you're like food to me." Seryoso niyang sabi.

"...." -Ako yan. Di parin ako makapagsalita -_________-

"I think I might die if I don't have you."  Ang init ng mukha ko. Pusha! -_______- Ano ba pinagsasabe neto? Ang bilis nanaman tuloy ng tibok ng puso ko. Bat kanina kay Francis, hindi naman ganto 'to. Pero pag kay Yun Ju, lupet ng kabog. Taena lungs.

"Corny." Sabi ko sabay alis ng tingin sa kanya. Kanina pa kame magkatinginan, nakakailang na. -__________-

"Hahaha. Sungit mo talaga, Charlotte. That's why I love you."

"Labo mo rin e, no? Mahal mo ko kase masungit ako? Tss." 

"'Cause you're being yourself. Though people hate that personality of yours, they can't change the fact that you're true than them." 

"Baduy ng words of wisdom mo."

"Ewan ko ba, kung ano-ano na pinagsasabi ko mula ng mainlove ako. Ganun siguro yung love, no?" Siguro nga. Ako ren eh. Kung ano-ano pinagsasabi. Pero teka.. HINDI NAMAN AKO INLOVE AH?! DIBA?! Napatingin naman ako ulit kay Yun Ju, nakatingin parin siya saken.

"If you said so." -Ako

"Charlotte, I won't give up on you. I'll do my best so that I'll be the one you'll choose. But, whatever you're decision is, I'll respect it. It's just that, I love you."

"You keep saying you love me. (-_- )"

"I'm just want you to know what I feel for you. I'm not waiting for an answer, don't worry."

 

Ngumiti siya. Ano ba 'to? Yung puso ko, fuck! Humarap ulit ako sa sea. Wala na yung araw, pinalitan na ng buwan. Medyo madilim na, pero may liwanag parin yung buwan.

 

Pakiramdam ko talaga, nagbabago ako. Parang nagiiba yung mga sinasabi ko, yung ibang words na lumalabas sa bibig ko, hindi ko naman yun nasasabi dati. Aish. I'm not INLOVE. Pero, sabi ni Mom saken dati.. "Love can change you." I don't want to believe her at first. But this time, I think it's true. Am I inlove? NO. -_____________-

 

Aish. Sino ba pipiliin ko sa dalawang 'to? Si Francis, he's my best friend. I don't want to ruin our friendship just because of this. Si Yun Ju, I don't know but.. He's somewhat becoming special to me. And I don't know why or how.

 

Fck. Charlotte, don't worry to much. You have plenty of time. Just go on with it. Wait for your heart to say something. Wait for it to tell you who you will choose.

 

PUTA. Ang baduy ko na. -_____________-
